     **Odoo Telegram Integration**  
**Steps to configure:**  
 **1\. Create Telegram Bot**

* Talk to [@BotFather](https://t.me/BotFather)  
* Use /newbot and follow instructions  
* Save the generated Bot Token

### **2\. Setup Bot in Odoo**

* Go to Telegram Integration  \>Configuration  
* Fill in the token,name and chat id   
* Click send message  
 **![][image1]**

### 3\. Set Webhook

Install the ngrok for local testing to setup webhook setup for receiving messages

Install ngrok   
Run in command prompt with this ngrok http 8069  
![][image2]  
Copy that forwarding url   
**curl \-X POST "https://api.telegram.org/bot\<your\_token\>/setWebhook" \\**  
     **\-d "url=[https://yourdomain.com/telegram/webhook](https://yourdomain.com/telegram/webhook)"**

**curl \--location 'https://api.telegram.org/bot7786052175:AAHO\_DQ9H4GlINQWEGDDxCg9l0cLOhB01-g/setWebhook' \\**

**\--header 'Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded' \\**

**\--data-urlencode 'url=https://6070-103-90-211-150.ngrok-free.app/telegram/webhook'**

**Then we able to send and receive messages**
